FBIS4-8159 "dreeu070_d_94007" FBIS-EEU-94-070 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 SLOVAKIA Defense Minister Talks With Romanian Army Chief Defense Minister Talks With Romanian Army Chief LD1104180494 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1300 GMT 11 Apr 94 LD1104180494 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1300 GMT 11 Apr 94 Slovak BFN [Text] Defense Minister Pavol Kanis today received Lieutenant General Dumitru Cioflina, state secretary at the Romanian Ministry of National Defense and chief of staff of the armed forces of Romania, who is paying a two-day visit to Slovakia. They briefed each other on the structures of the armed forces, discussed possibilities of cooperation in the military sphere, and confirmed their interest in cooperation when modernizing weapons and arms systems.
